1
00:02:09,698 --> 00:02:11,389
You don't understand.

2
00:02:11,399 --> 00:02:13,631
Krypton's core is collapsing.

3
00:02:13,634 --> 00:02:15,836
We may only
have a matter of weeks.

4
00:02:15,843 --> 00:02:19,605
I warned you,
harvesting the core was suicide.

5
00:02:19,905 --> 00:02:21,907
It has accelerated
the process of implosion.

6
00:02:21,973 --> 00:02:26,677
Our energy reserves were exhausted,
what would you have us do, El?

7
00:02:26,678 --> 00:02:30,241
Look to the stars.
Like our ancestors did.

8
00:02:30,247 --> 00:02:32,273
There are habitable worlds
within reach.

9
00:02:32,299 --> 00:02:34,350
We can begin
by using the old outposts.

10
00:02:34,383 --> 00:02:37,853
Are seriously suggesting that
we evacuate the entire planet?

11
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:41,422
No, everybody here
is already dead.

12
00:02:42,557 --> 00:02:47,059
Give me the control of the codex,
I will ensure the survival of our race.

13
00:02:47,126 --> 00:02:52,130
There is still hope,
I have held that hope in my hand.

14
00:03:05,774 --> 00:03:10,711
- This council has been disbanded.
- On whose authority?

15
00:03:10,811 --> 00:03:12,812
Mine.

16
00:03:15,414 --> 00:03:19,327
The rest of you will be tried
and punished accordingly.

17
00:03:21,309 --> 00:03:23,721
What are you doing, Zod?!
This is madness!

18
00:03:23,764 --> 00:03:27,957
What I should done years ago! These
lawmakers with their endless debates

19
00:03:28,024 --> 00:03:30,326
have led Krypton to ruin!

20
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:36,262
And if your forces prevail?
You be the leader of nothing.

21
00:03:36,364 --> 00:03:40,942
Then join me, help me
save our race, we'll start anew.

22
00:03:40,994 --> 00:03:45,197
We'll sever the degenerated
bloodlines that led us to this state.

23
00:03:45,237 --> 00:03:48,840
And who will decide
which bloodline survives, Zod?

24
00:03:50,141 --> 00:03:51,942
You?

25
00:03:52,943 --> 00:03:57,624
Don't do this, El. The last thing
I want is for us to be enemies.

26
00:03:57,847 --> 00:04:00,649
You have abandoned the principles
that bound us together,

27
00:04:00,716 --> 00:04:03,918
You've taken up the sword
against your own people.

28
00:04:04,419 --> 00:04:09,922
I'll honor the man you once were, Zod.
Not this monster you've become.

29
00:04:13,292 --> 00:04:15,593
Take him away!

30
00:04:20,697 --> 00:04:25,863
<i>Sir, is everything all right?</i>
- Out of the way! I said..

31
00:04:41,485 --> 00:04:47,087
Get me to Lara.
Jor! Behind you!

32
00:04:50,554 --> 00:04:55,591
Lara, you have to ready the launch,
I will be with you as soon as I can.

33
00:05:49,699 --> 00:05:52,401
- Have you seen the codex?
- It's just beneath the central house.

34
00:05:52,501 --> 00:05:56,437
<i>But I'm compelled to warn you, reaching
the chambers is class B crime punishable</i>

35
00:05:56,537 --> 00:06:01,040
Nobody cares any more, Keelex!
The world is about to come to an end.

36
00:07:04,789 --> 00:07:09,993
Jor-el, by the authority
of General Zod, surrender the codex.

37
00:07:57,729 --> 00:08:00,598
Easy, Harraka.

38
00:08:19,779 --> 00:08:21,948
Did you find the world?

39
00:08:21,949 --> 00:08:23,049
We have.

40
00:08:23,082 --> 00:08:26,084
<i>Orbiting main sequence yellow star
just as you said.</i>

41
00:08:28,119 --> 00:08:31,618
Young star.
His cells would drink its radiation.

42
00:08:34,725 --> 00:08:37,167
It has a seemingly
intelligent population.

43
00:08:38,118 --> 00:08:41,020
He will be an outcast, a freak.

44
00:08:42,888 --> 00:08:46,090
They'll kill him.
- How?

45
00:08:46,324 --> 00:08:48,826
He'll be a god to them.

46
00:08:49,867 --> 00:08:52,869
What if the ship doesn't make it?

47
00:08:53,297 --> 00:08:55,099
He will die out there.

48
00:08:55,331 --> 00:08:57,033
Alone.

49
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,202
I can't do it.

50
00:09:00,235 --> 00:09:03,729
I thought I could, but...
now that it's here...

51
00:09:04,398 --> 00:09:09,601
Krypton is doomed.
It's his only chance now.

52
00:09:09,708 --> 00:09:12,711
It's our people's only hope.

53
00:09:12,964 --> 00:09:14,022
What is it, Keelex?

54
00:09:14,048 --> 00:09:16,596
<i>Five attack ships
converging from the east.</i>

55
00:09:16,681 --> 00:09:19,183
<i>Citadel’s defenses
are being scanned and evaluated.</i>

56
00:09:19,269 --> 00:09:21,770
I'll upload the codex.
- No, wait.

57
00:09:22,609 --> 00:09:24,117
Lara...

58
00:09:24,153 --> 00:09:26,855
Just... let me look at him.

59
00:09:30,325 --> 00:09:33,027
I'll never get to see him walk.

60
00:09:34,727 --> 00:09:37,496
Never hear him say our names.

61
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:45,903
Out there amongst the stars...

62
00:09:47,171 --> 00:09:50,173
he will live.

63
00:10:46,716 --> 00:10:49,585
Goodbye, my son.

64
00:10:49,596 --> 00:10:51,916
I hope some dreams
travel with you.

65
00:11:30,416 --> 00:11:33,719
Concentrate fire on the main door.

66
00:11:48,993 --> 00:11:51,791
<i>Lady Lara, the phantom drives
are coming on-line</i>

67
00:11:51,812 --> 00:11:53,616
Proceed to ignition.

68
00:11:54,934 --> 00:11:58,637
We have identified an engine ignition
within the citadel.

69
00:11:59,386 --> 00:12:00,987
A launch...

70
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:04,342
Hold this platform, Commander.

71
00:12:16,551 --> 00:12:22,589
