birth in centuries.

77
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:45,140
And he will be free.
Free to forge his own destiny.

78
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:47,641
Heresy!

79
00:12:49,209 --> 00:12:50,710
Destroy it!

80
00:13:43,808 --> 00:13:46,678
Lara, listen to me!

81
00:13:46,719 --> 00:13:49,722
The Codex is Krypton's future.

82
00:13:50,389 --> 00:13:52,390
Abort the launch!

83
00:14:43,529 --> 00:14:48,900
Your son, Lara...
Where have you sent him?

84
00:14:51,539 --> 00:14:55,142
His name is Kal.

85
00:14:55,439 --> 00:14:57,440
Son of El.

86
00:15:00,209 --> 00:15:03,939
And he is beyond your reach.

87
00:15:13,219 --> 00:15:16,354
Bring that ship down.

88
00:15:22,826 --> 00:15:24,327
<i>Target locked.</i>

89
00:15:36,236 --> 00:15:40,039
Lay down your weapons,
your forces are surrounded.

90
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:54,444
General Zod, for the crimes
of murder and high treason,

91
00:15:54,717 --> 00:15:59,286
the Council has sentenced you
and your fellow insurgents

92
00:15:59,334 --> 00:16:03,438
